{"name":"Harps Walks-on-Water","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"any race","alignment":"any alignment","hitDice":"7","armorName":"studded leather","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (splint)","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"38 (7d8 + 7)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"11","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"14","intPoints":"12","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"8","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"3","customCr":"3 (700 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The veteran can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The veteran regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the veteran can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the veteran can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The veteran can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the veteran's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the veteran's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the veteran dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Keen Sight and Smell","desc":"[MON] has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight or smell."},{"name":"Feline Agility","desc":"[MON]' reflexes and agility allow him to move with a burst of speed. When [MON] moves on his  turn in combat, he can double his speed until the end of the turn. Once he uses this trait, he can't use it again until he moves 0 feet on one of his turns."},{"name":"Pounce","desc":"If [MON] moves at least 20 ft. straight toward a target and then hits it with a claw attack on the same turn, the target takes an extra [1D6] slashing damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on a DC [DEX SAVE] Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. If the target is prone, [MON] can make another claw attack against it as a bonus action."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes two claw attacks."},{"name":"Claws","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] piercing damage."},{"name":"Light Crossbow","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D8] piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Nimble Escape","desc":"[MON] can take the Disengage or Hide action as a bonus action on each of his turns."},{"name":"Parry","desc":"The [MON] adds 2 to its AC against one melee attack that would hit it. To do so, the [MON] must see the attacker and be wielding a melee weapon."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Uncanny Dodge (1/day)","desc":"When [MON] is hit with an attack roll he can use his reaction to halve the damage."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"acrobatics","stat":"dex"},{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"sleight of Hand","stat":"dex"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Harps","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":3,"damage":[]}